author: fhanik
msg: Update configurations options, this new feature allows a specific <Context> to overwrite what cluster manager is used by specifying a <Manager> element inside the context element and the cluster will be notified of it.
This allows for a cleaner config, as the cluster does no longer have to forward all manager settings, and allows documentation to be much clearer on what settings are available.
